name: The origin III (Black Edition)
description: This is a creation that I have entirely realized personally in 3D, it took me a lot of time and I hope you will appreciate it I wanted to represent on this work a certain balance between men and women. The theme was turned on the access of women in the world of mathematics, so I did not want to represent only the female or male sex but rather both in a particular staging It turns out that mathematics is everywhere in our lives, even in our anatomical conception. (2000x2000 pixels / 6.85Mo)
